<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ de jiā shì shì fèng yé hé huá, hái shì shì fèng dà hé nà biān de shén?
 nǐ de jiā shì fǒu yǒu shén de jì tán, tóng fēn xiǎng zhǔ qí miào de ēn diǎn?
 cháng qīn jìn zhǔ yé sū, tā shì wǒ men shēng mìng de quán yuán.
 nǐ yào shí cháng shí cháng shěng chá, miǎn dé lǐ miàn de guāng hēi àn.
 yào bǎo shǒu bǎo shǒu nǐ xīn, shèng guò bǎo shǒu bǎo shǒu yī qiè.
 nǐ de jiā yào shì fèng yé hé huá, yīn tā zài yī qiè zhī shàng.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ de jiā yào shì fèng yé hé huá 迦南987</title>
